@startuml
title User Profile Consultation Flow

|User|
start
:Login to the application;

|System|
:Authenticate credentials;
:Redirect to home page;
:Fetch data from **user_info** table;
note right
  Fields retrieved:
  * Registration date
  * Neuro entry date
  * Neuro status
  * Protocol
  * State
  * Prosthetist
end note

if (Data found?) then (yes)
  :Render Profile View;
  |User|
  :View personal information;
else (no)
  |System|
  :Display "Profile data not found" error;
  :Redirect to home page with error message;
endif

stop
@enduml